Hey all, not super familiar with HubL but trying to dynamically render a menu based on a contacts property....any idea why this code doesn't actually render a different menu and just falls through to the bottom one?

``` {% if request_contact.is_logged_in %}
        {% menu "top_menu" id=80838546218, flyouts="false", max_levels="2", label="Header Login" %}
        {% else %}
        {% menu "top_menu" id=86309392450, flyouts="false", max_levels="2", label="Header Logout" %}
        {% endif %}```
It's odd because if I put something like:

``` {% if request_contact.is_logged_in %}
        cats
        {% menu "top_menu" id=80838546218, flyouts="false", max_levels="2", label="Header Login" %}
        {% else %}
        {% menu "top_menu" id=86309392450, flyouts="false", max_levels="2", label="Header Logout" %}
        {% endif %}```
it'll render cats and then the bottom menu
